{"tid":1505820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【錯台重開】不要說：「停」試著說：「慢慢疏開」","createTime":"2019-08-25T15:46:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T06:40:34.000Z","uid":71812,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5995a01004340e1d07b97302355f86c685f462ab","tid":1505820,"uid":71812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T15:46:18.000Z","msg":"一直以來，前線都唔夠位走<br />\n大家要知道現場會有時差<br />\n你慢慢退要五分鐘先傳到最後<br />\n就算一開始企得疏<br />\n三次之後就會逼到仆街走唔切<br />\n原因係叫停大家就會企哂係到<br />\n所以麻煩大家改改口<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">叫「慢慢tun開」<br />\n等後排退開啲<br />\n前排先有位走<br />\n唔該大家</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"ec87e6d84d456887b77071f0f2a78aa7347db9de","tid":1505820,"uid":71812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T15:46:39.000Z","msg":"自推10次 1"},{"pid":"35e74e6e7c56e5d3288662390a1cba8a4ee7a119","tid":1505820,"uid":71812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T15:46:56.000Z","msg":"自推10次2"},{"pid":"42f6dc22bf874e68317848f5073bb8a133a64294","tid":1505820,"uid":71812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T15:47:09.000Z","msg":"自推3/10"},{"pid":"5c011e6a18c64116dac047f805a5923bf81404e3","tid":1505820,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T15:48:09.000Z","msg":"【置頂】828 metoo集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1505524\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1505524</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6359a696a65f890c096e41fcb64c996bd686b057","tid":1505820,"uid":71812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T15:51:42.000Z","msg":"自推4/10"},{"pid":"a7283cceb1e9311c641c3e24cd9cfca2e7d184bd","tid":1505820,"uid":182114,"like":0